# Pi agents monorepo

**Read `AGENTS.md` first.** Production runtime is `pi-agent-core` + `pi-ai`, not Pi CLI discovery.

- One agent per `packages/<kebab-name>/`; scaffold with `pnpm run new-agent`.
- `_template` is migration scaffold (CLI shape); new agents target SDK tools + `SKILL.md`.
- Design reference: `docs/architecture.md`. Third-party deps: `docs/third-party-extensions.md`. Contributor process: `CONTRIBUTING.md`.

Before marking work complete: `pnpm run validate` and `pnpm run typecheck`.
